sub_title: Freelance Digital Marketing | Performance Marketer | Pinterest & Instagram | DTC
summary:
My name is Samantha and I am a Pinterest marketing expert with five years of experience in the field. I earned my Bachelor's degree in Marketing at the University of Ottawa and went on to pursue a Master's degree in Marketing at the University of Amsterdam, which equipped me with extensive knowledge and expertise in digital marketing strategies.

Over the course of my career, I have had the pleasure of working closely with various companies to increase and optimize their Pinterest presence. I am passionate about crafting customized Pinterest marketing strategies that cater to each client's unique goals and target audience.

My expertise lies in understanding how to leverage Pinterest's visual platform to drive traffic, leads, and sales for businesses of all sizes. I am committed to staying up-to-date with the latest trends and best practices in the field of Pinterest marketing to deliver the most effective strategies to my clients. 

My ultimate goal is to help businesses achieve their Pinterest marketing objectives and make a positive impact on their bottom line.
